'''Chintassa grass''' was a [[Plant/Legends|plant]] grown in specialized [[Farm/Legends|farms]] on several [[Planet/Legends|planets]]. With a spicy flavor and nutritional properties it was considered a delicacy. It was usually served marinated and steamed. It came in an "angel hair" variety.

